492
00:44:31,403 --> 00:44:34,198
- Jika kau gagal?
- Kau membenciku, bukan?

493
00:44:34,281 --> 00:44:35,324
Aku akan berhenti.

494
00:44:35,908 --> 00:44:38,869
Aku tak peduli soal pengunduran dirimu

495
00:44:40,079 --> 00:44:42,081
