513
00:47:00,385 --> 00:47:02,304
Dal-geon, kau pasti lapar.

514
00:47:33,544 --> 00:47:35,045
Astaga.

515
00:47:37,339 --> 00:47:39,007
Nasi gorengnya terlalu banyak.

516
00:47:51,103 --> 00:47:52,396
Siapa itu?

517
00:47:52,479 --> 00:47:54,231
Dal-geon, ini aku.

518
00:47:56,149 --> 00:47:57,317
Go Hae-ri?

519
00:48:01,697 --> 00:48:03,949
