00:48:21,300 --> 00:48:23,635
Untunglah aku di sini.

527
00:48:23,719 --> 00:48:26,889
Kau masak banyak. Ada ham juga!

528
00:48:32,019 --> 00:48:33,312
AYAM TTOBONGEE

529
00:48:40,736 --> 00:48:43,238
