00:49:49,388 --> 00:49:50,347
Apa?

540
00:49:50,430 --> 00:49:52,683
Hei. Pelan-pelan.

541
00:49:55,894 --> 00:49:57,062
Ada apa denganmu?

542
00:49:59,940 --> 00:50:01,566
Aku mencoba tenang.

543
00:50:03,026 --> 00:50:04,653
